Hi Sree, 

Just jumping in with the technical details of this request. 

The go-live sequence can be done in a single day. There are 2 phases, prep and go live. The prep phase can be done ASAP as this will not launch the new website, but will enable us to generate the SSL certificate for your domain. Please add the below DNS records to: sgua.com.au

TXT record 
Name/host: _cf-custom-hostname
Value: 6da3e961-52b3-4509-b473-fb111d236e06

CNAME record
Name/host: _acme-challenge.sgua.com.au
Domain name: sgua.com.au.kinstavalidation.app

Once this is done, let me know and I will verify and our end and provide the final DNS records to make the site live. Please let me know if you have any questions.

@heath can you please assist me with below?

I'd like to provide a simple explanation for Sree so he can plan accordingly.
